      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a concours-grade specimen featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies, paired with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates to ensure structural integrity. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, benefiting from a refreshed suspension with factory-spec bushings and Bilstein dampers. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains a deep luster with zero oxidative damage or panel misalignment. The M-Variable Differential Lock operates silently, providing optimal torque vectoring. This is a collector-quality example with a documented service history and zero mechanical compromises.",
      "price": 46500.0,
